column2: SELECT Top #   m.ID, m.RAdeg AS ra1, m.DEdeg AS dec1,   n.objid, n.distance, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.z, s.zErr,   s.zWarning, s.class, s.subclass,    s.ra AS ra2, s.dec AS dec2 FROM MyDB.nepwise AS m    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.RAdeg, m.DEdeg, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS s ON n.objid=s.specObjID     AND s.z > #
